Package com.st.st25sdk.type2

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    STType2PasswordInterface
    Defines an API to handle a STMicroelectronics Type2 tag featuring passwords
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CCFile
    Defines methods to handle a NFC Forum Capability Container file
    CCFileType2
    Defines methods to handle a NFC Forum Type2 Capability Container file
    DynamicLockType2
    Defines methods to handle Dynamic Lock Bits of a NFC Forum Type2 tag
    DynamicLockType2Configuration
    Defines methods to handle Dynamic Lock Bits Configuration based on Lock Control TLV informations or Default Configuration of a NFC Forum Type2 tag
    ReservedAreaType2Configuration
    Defines methods to handle Reseved Area Configuration based on Memory Control TLV informations of a NFC Forum Type2 tag
    StaticLockType2
    Defines methods to handle Static Lock bytes of a NFC Forum Type2 tag Static area = 4 bytes CC file + 48 bytes of User Memory from byte address 12 to 63 (block 3 : CC File + blocks 4 to 15) NFCForum-TS-T2T-1.0 specification
    STType2Tag
    Defines required methods to handle a ST Type2 tag
    Type2Tag
    Defines required methods to handle a NFC Forum Type2 tag
